text: Brugg is a city in the Swiss canton of Aargau. It is the capital of the district of Brugg. Since 2010, Umiken has been part of the city. On 1 January 2020 the municipality of Schinznach-Bad merged into Brugg. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Municipalities in Brugg Category:Cities in Switzerland
